Package util

Utility classes to generate links between two data sets according to criteria.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
App Handles the interlinking process from A to Z.
DataSet Abstract class managing a data set from any origin.
Linkage Abstract class interlinking two data sets according to criteria.
Output Abstract class to process the result of the interlinking.
RDFApp Helps handling the interlinking with RDF data.
RDFDataSet A data set stored locally which lasts only for runtime.
RDFOutput Exports the interlinking as RDFXML.
SesameApp Helps handling the interlinking with Sesame data sets.
SesameDataSet A data set stored inside a local or remote Sesame server.
SesameOutput Deprecated.  
SPARQLApp Helps handling the interlinking using SPARQL.
SPARQLDataSet A data set accessed using a SPARQL endpoint.
SPARQLOutput Updates a SPARQL endpoint using SPARQL queries.
StandardLinkage Links two data sets according to two predicates.
TailorLinkage Links two datasets according to fully customizable queries.
TypedLinkage Links two data sets according to two predicates and two data types.
 

Package util Description

Utility classes to generate links between two data sets according to criteria.
